Description_lang: One of your abilities is improved, based on the weapon you are wielding:|cFFFFFFFFMaces|r allow you to cast Victory Rush without killing an enemy, and killing an enemy will reset its cooldown.$?s118038[|cFFFFFFFFSwords|r reduce the cooldown of Die by the Sword by ${$264085s1/-1000} sec, and you will counterattack all melees against you while it is active.][|cFFFF0000Sword bonus unlocked at Level 36.|r]$?s5246[|cFFFFFFFFAxes|r and |cFFFFFFFFPolearms|r reduce the cooldown of Rallying Cry and Intimidating Shout by $266143s1%, and increase their duration by $266143s2%.][|cFFFF0000Axe and Polearm bonus unlocked at Level 70.|r]
